### 7. UPDATE: Inventory map — traffic batch overlay

In `Inventory.tsx`, load traffic batch on map view open:
```ts
const [trafficMap, setTrafficMap] = useState<Map<number, number>>(new Map());

useEffect(() => {
  if (view !== 'map') return;
  fetchTrafficBatch().then((t) => {
    setTrafficMap(new Map(t.map((tr) => [tr.id, tr.trafficScore])));
  });
}, [view]);
```

In `MapView`, pass `trafficMap` as prop, update CircleMarker fillOpacity:
```ts
const score = trafficMap.get(u.id) ?? 65;
fillOpacity: u.status === 'maintenance' ? 0.25 : 0.4 + (score / 100) * 0.55,
```

